They come to their senses,
shocked with reality.

59
00:05:25,226 --> 00:05:29,492
That's how I deal with them:
I start with Piaget. I'm polite, I'm kind.

60
00:05:29,697 --> 00:05:33,224
I give love and expect
to get love...

61
