66
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:52,220
- Fine. Welcome.
- Thank you.

67
00:05:52,755 --> 00:05:54,985
Come on in.

68
00:05:56,492 --> 00:06:00,520
Before Sergio's tenure,
at the wee hours...

69
00:06:00,731 --> 00:06:04,189
that lobby there...

70
00:06:04,401 --> 00:06:08,337
