I used to join them, too.

73
00:06:15,146 --> 00:06:19,412
About 1 am, I'd get insomniac,
so I'd go down, too.

74
00:06:19,618 --> 00:06:22,247
We all ate, the doormen drank...

75
00:06:22,455 --> 00:06:25,856
