I just wanna wait a little,
cause he's too eager.

192
00:14:48,204 --> 00:14:53,642
Everyday he sends me e- mails,
calls, wires me money...

193
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:57,004
- How do you call him?
- "My chocolate baby", he calls me.

194
00:14:57,213 --> 00:14:59,579
I call him "my chocolate white".

195
00:15:00,384 --> 00:15:04,821
He's really cool.
AIways joking, you know?

196
