US' most famous organizations.

198
00:15:12,864 --> 00:15:16,595
- Is he single, married, widowed?
- He's single, and he's mine!

199
00:15:18,203 --> 00:15:20,364
He's got a beautiful son,
who loves me dearly!

200
00:15:20,572 --> 00:15:22,301
- Does his son know you?
- Yes, he does.

201
00:15:22,507 --> 00:15:25,306
I know his mom.
His son came to visit, she didn't.

202
00:15:25,511 --> 00:15:27,672
She sends me e- malls.

203
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:31,372
It seems he has a huge house,
and his wife left him.

204
00:15:31,584 --> 00:15:35,112
My poor baby,
his wife was a neurotic.

205
00:15:35,322 --> 00:15:39,019
She took off with a lover,
and left him with their son...

206
00:15:39,226 --> 00:15:42,662
and a huge trauma.
He's been separated for 2 years.

207
00:15:42,863 --> 00:15:48,029
I think he found in me
what he'd been looking for.

208
00:15:48,236 --> 00:15:51,433
I have a dream, cause when
I Ieft home, my mom said:

209
00:15:51,906 --> 00:15:55,467
"You wanna move in with
your cousin? Fine!"

210
00:15:55,676 --> 00:16:00,444
"You'll be back in a week,
begging for a plate of food."

211
00:16:01,149 --> 00:16:03,413
As I'm really proud, I said:

212
00:16:03,619 --> 00:16:07,316
"Mom, apart from being a hooker
or a killer..."

213
00:16:07,522 --> 00:16:10,788
