in my womb for 3 days.

226
00:16:56,910 --> 00:17:02,849
On the 4th, my temperature
was, like, 1O7 F.

227
00:17:03,050 --> 00:17:07,249
When I recovered, my mom said:
"Let's go home."

228
00:17:07,455 --> 00:17:11,789
I said: "Maybe you forgot
you'd told me...

229
00:17:11,993 --> 00:17:14,359
that I couldn't stay home
with a baby."

230
00:17:14,562 --> 00:17:17,087
"So, even without one,
you won't want me there."

231
00:17:17,298 --> 00:17:19,199
"I love you, but..."

232
00:17:19,401 --> 00:17:22,598
I couldn't bear to see
my mom cry, I'd cry, too.

233
00:17:23,305 --> 00:17:26,604
Now I'm Renata, and that's it.
I'm #1 in Brazil.

234
00:17:27,509 --> 00:17:31,037
Nobody will ever let me
down again.

235
00:17:52,303 --> 00:17:54,499
My music keeps me entertained.

236
00:17:54,706 --> 00:17:59,507
I've already played a little
keyboard today.

237
00:17:59,711 --> 00:18:04,375
I enjoy singing.
I used to sing a lot.

238
